data.description:
Introducing this captivating Four-bedroom, three-bathroom brick ranch, ideally positioned in an enviable location. Nestled within a serene neighborhood, this residence offers not only the charm of a classic brick exterior but also the allure of a finished basement, featuring an additional bedroom and bathroom.
Step into a spacious living environment adorned with timeless brickwork, blending both elegance and durability. The main floor boasts three thoughtfully designed bedrooms, providing ample space for rest and relaxation. Two well-appointed bathrooms ensure convenience and comfort for the entire household.
A well-equipped kitchen awaits, promising culinary adventures and gatherings with loved ones. The inviting living areas are perfect for both intimate family moments and entertaining guests.
Descend into the finished basement, where possibilities abound. An additional bedroom and bathroom create a versatile living space, ideal for extended family or guests. This space is ready to adapt to your unique needs, whether it be a home office, gym, or entertainment area.
Outside, enjoy the benefits of an incredible location, offering proximity to amenities, schools, and leisure facilities. The allure of this property is enhanced by its attractive exterior, spacious interior, and the valuable bonus of a finished basement—a true embodiment of comfort, style, and functionality. Embrace the potential this home holds and make it your own today. Buyer/Buyers agent to verify all information take from a third party.
